mand worked [date]") beats vendor docs; contradictions between playbook reality resolved toward reality playbook re-dated. business's records highest-trust layer. **Stale loud.** Past staleness horizon, playbook's guidance flagged any output using ("per playbook dated [old date] verify before trusting"). Sibling skills inherit flag; deploy following stale playbook says checklist. **Connectors named, assumed.** playbook lists MCP/connector automates platform (plan §5: Harness.io CI/CD, Datadog telemetry proposed deployment suggest-connectors pattern). Absent connector manual mechanics documented, capability degraded loudly (quinn's principle inherited). **Marketplace per-platform skills import playbooks.** business runs platform good marketplace skill, import verbatim-with-provenance playbook's machinery (quinn's webapp-testing pattern) playbook wraps business's specifics date. **Charter binds mechanics.** Playbook commands run under locked plans (Rail sandboxes (Rail 2); any playbook step touching data destructively written prepared-script-for-operator step (Rail playbook never instruct agent run one. · of=Playbooks follow `assets/platform-playbook-template.md`. use, agents cite date section: "per [host] playbook §Deploy (as [date])" date travels citation. · pr=**Method durable; platforms dated** volatility split portability mechanism., **Ground truth beats vendor docs** verified records re-date playbooks; reality wins contradictions., **Stale knowledge announces itself** horizons loud flags; silent staleness failure mode skill exists kill., **One playbook platform, business** swapping businesses swaps playbooks, never skills., **No undated platform claims** anywhere, any Engineering output., **Playbooks never instruct charter breaches** destructive steps operator-script steps construction. · f=playbook platform stack-profile names sibling skills run method-only manual verification host step; writing playbook becomes dated task, seeded first verified run., Stack-pro